Package: crew.ssh
Title: 'crew' Launcher Plugin for Running on a Remote System with 'ssh'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bill", "Denney", email="wdenney@humanpredictions.com", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-5759-428X"))
Description: In computationally demanding analysis projects, statisticians and
  data scientists may asynchronously deploy long-running tasks to remote
  systems by 'ssh'. This extends the 'crew' package with worker launcher plugins
  for remote systems by 'ssh'.
